  "id": "3fcc9b35-39e4-44c0-a2ad-9e82b6902b31",
  "description": "Detects specific commands commonly used to remove or empty the syslog. Which is a technique often used by attacker as a method to hide their tracks\n",
  "sigmafile": "",
